style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125529\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \"> &gt; </span></span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125530\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; \">”，收音机将自动搜索并保存可用频道。</span>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125531\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n<p class=\"p4\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\">\n<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none; font-size: 10.5pt; \">首次开启收音机时，收音机将自动搜索并保存可用频道。</span>\n<br>\n</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>2.</span><a name=\"_task_listen_to_fm_radio.xml-chtext\"><span> </span><span>收听节目</span></a>\n</span></p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>在主屏幕，点击“实用工具 &gt; 收音机”。</span>\n</span></p>\n<table class=\"t1\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125532\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"td2\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>打开外放功能。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125533\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"td2\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>关闭或打开收音机。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125534\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"td2\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>进入上一个可用频道。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125535\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"td2\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>进入下一个可用频道。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125536\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"td2\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>收藏频道。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125537\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"td2\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>进入设置界面：搜索和查看频道列表、查看收藏的频道、设置定时关闭收音机的时长。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n<span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125538\" style=\"width:3.0in;height:3.0in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n<table class=\"t1\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125539\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"td2\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>打开外放功能。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125540\" style=\"width:0.22569445in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"></span></p>\n      </td>\n      <td class=\"td2\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span>关闭或打开收音机。</span>\n      </span></p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"r1\">\n      <td class=\"td1\">\n      <p class=\"p7\">\n      <span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=125541\" style